{"tid":533830,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"請珍惜CR7...（認真）","createTime":"2018-01-19T08:06:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T08:24:46.000Z","uid":57035,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"212ef9d7fbd662c550d164545c31dcc54bb2c19e","tid":533830,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:06:07.000Z","msg":"細個開始睇波果陣好撚憎49000，覺得史譚、簡東拿、堅尼好撚茅（當年堅尼一野踢低holland），次次進攻都好似教科書一樣既戰術好悶<br />\n<br />\n到佢地退晒休，先知果D老練既技術／走位係好野黎<br />\n<br />\n史鳩斯既獨特節奏、巴夫斯（全盛時期）既神救、費格遜對風筒既執著，都係到退休／收左皮先發現佢地原來咁撚勁<br />\n<br />\n連登仔好多人都反c朗，但係老實講佢既TIP IN技術、決心、對比賽既執著，冇人比得上佢（我覺得依家尼馬&gt;&gt;C朗）[2]<br />\n<br />\n我諗C朗最多都係打多3、4年就退休，其實睇得1場得1場，好好珍惜<br />\n<br />\n利申：山度士賀夫年代南華迷"},{"pid":"d3c27b4417648cb74a88888c27cbf0a8d44bc388","tid":533830,"uid":33601,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/161020_98b83eb9bd02c2bf675849062b21aa34.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F161020_98b83eb9bd02c2bf675849062b21aa34.gif&h=32eb194c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25f511ef58b8809a9550bdab7e245b248a246b92","tid":533830,"uid":128007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:15:22.000Z","msg":"岩弓口"},{"pid":"fb573d08485f3079bf744b1d946bf2211409a549","tid":533830,"uid":128007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:15:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩弓口</blockquote><br />\n阿"},{"pid":"0aeb9b3911fa24303b6bddfe0bcc29a7477e674d","tid":533830,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3c27b4417648cb74a88888c27cbf0a8d44bc388","tid":533830,"uid":33601,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/161020_98b83eb9bd02c2bf675849062b21aa34.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F201